** 长子：耿军<ref name=xinzg/>，是[[耿乐|耿乐]]的父亲。
** 次子：[[张郎郎|张郎郎]]<ref name=xinzg>{{Cite web|url =http://history.people.com.cn/GB/198819/206832/13832020.html|title =张寥寥口述：父亲张仃——包装新中国|author =|date =2011-01-27|publisher =人民网|language =|accessdate =|quote =|archive-date =2020-05-18|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200518044117/http://history.people.com.cn/GB/198819/206832/13832020.html}}</ref>
** 三子：张大伟<ref name=xinzg/>
** 四子：[[张寥寥|张寥寥]]<ref name=xinzg/>
** 五子：张沛沛<ref name=xinzg/>
* 第二任妻子：[[灰娃|灰娃]]。1985年张仃的妻子陈布文病逝，后来张仃与灰娃结婚<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2010-02-23/13482880159.shtml |title = 张仃与灰娃的诗画人生 |author =  |date = 2010-02-23 |publisher = 新浪 |language =  |accessdate =  |quote =  |archive-date = 2021-02-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210216051733/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2010-02-23/13482880159.shtml }}</ref>。

